    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Cool School Preschool, located in Malibu, CA, offers an in-home Montessori-based educational program. The school supports learning self-help skills, sensorial play, math, and pre-reading skills. The students are grouped into age-appropriate classes and learn a curated curriculum. They also have access to artistic expression, music, and story time. Physical development is promoted through gymnastics, dance, team sports, and other activities. </p>
